"[START]\n"
"This app can be used to read a script from the screen, just paste or open a "
"text file.\n"
"Anything between square brackets like [this] is highlighted.\n"
"\n"
"[Customization]\n"
"The font, color of the text and highlights can be customized."
msgstr ""
"[Comincia]\n"
"Questa applicazione può essere usata per leggere un testo dallo schermo, "
